oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 31st Annual Festival WIBA at Cotillion Ballroom (16873)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: West, Dottie, 1932-1991; Dickens, Little Jimmy, 1920-2015; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on light brown) announcing the 31st Annual Festival WIBA featuring Dottie West and Little Jimmy Dickens at the Cotillion Ballroom in Wichita, Kansas on October 3. Poster features metal photoplate of Dottie West and Little Jimmy Dickens. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/40282.
